headline: Box Tops for Education Celebrates Teacher Appreciation Month with $300,000 Award to Schools Nationwide
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, May 01, 2025--Every May, Box Tops for Education champions Teacher Appreciation Month and celebrates the educators who go above and beyond for their students — and this year, Box Tops is highlighting its recent $300,000 award to schools nationwide. The funding — provided in December 2024 to 10 different schools across the country — is now being brought to life this spring, transforming classrooms, playgrounds, and student experiences through educator-led initiatives.
